{"tid":721057,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國一名學生玩日系恐怖gal game被精神污染自殺身亡","createTime":"2018-06-28T12:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T12:12:28.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"908edb04151ce0c7a02a7414200731866541b41d","tid":721057,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:14:17.000Z","msg":"英國大曼徹斯特郡（Greater Manchester）一名15歲少年，疑似玩了一款日系風格的網路戀愛、恐怖遊戲後自盡。死子父親指，遊戲令兒子無法抽身，嚴重影響他的心理狀態，害兒子踏上不歸路，呼籲家長留意。有玩家稱，遊戲有「精神污染」情節，如：女主角們會互相嘲弄詛咒，甚至不管怎麼玩、不管做出什麼樣的選擇，部分女主角一定會自盡，影響玩家心情。<br />\n<br />\n15歲的溫斯尼（Ben Walmsley）今年2月過世，死因庭正調查他的死因。溫斯尼的49歲父親達勒（Darren）認為，兒子是被一款名為《心跳文學部!》（Doki Doki Literature Club!）的網路遊戲「深深吸引」，不時在睡夢中醒來，查看遊戲傳來的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n《心跳文學部!》是一款由美國開發團隊「Team Salvato」開發，去年9月發行的日系戀愛遊戲，由於故事內設恐怖元素（女角色們會自殘）而備受好評，去年曾獲選IGN最佳遊戲獎最佳冒險遊戲第二名，今年也拿下西南偏南（SXSW）遊戲獎的馬修&middot;克倫普文化創新獎。《PC Gamer》更形容它是「2017年最令人驚訝的遊戲」。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲背景描述，一名男高中生加入學校的文學部，與4名女性成員相處的故事，角色交流會根據玩家選擇的對話或行動，而有所轉變。達勒認為：「這令人著迷，他們看來很真實&hellip;又是免費下載，一旦你玩，就無法脫身，角色會以朋友的身份看待你，甚至愛上你，還會交任務給你完成，如果你不做，她們會變得很兇。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》沒有有提及，溫斯尼如何死亡，而達勒相信，兒子的死與遊戲內容有關，「對父母來說很難，但要提高警覺。雖然還沒有確認，但我相信遊戲與他（溫斯尼）的死有關。遊戲角色很真實，慢慢令你越陷越深。」<br />\n<br />\n報導指，遊戲雖然有警告字句，提醒玩家「劇情有令人不安的內容」，不過死因庭法官仍特別警告巿議會和學校，要小心這款遊戲為學童帶來的心理影響。警方則呼籲家長．定時檢查子女電腦的網站瀏覽記錄，「我們相信，這遊戲對兒童和年輕人存有風險，尤其對一些情緒脆弱或有精神問題的人」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.zerochan.net/Yuri.%28Doki.Doki.Literature.Club%21%29.full.2261716.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.zerochan.net%2FYuri.%2528Doki.Doki.Literature.Club%2521%2529.full.2261716.png&h=46755a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ldabEuEvqxI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FldabEuEvqxI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=af16021f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/doki-doki-literature-club/images/5/5b/Yuri_death_scene_3.png/revision/latest?cb=20171112093758\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fdoki-doki-literature-club%2Fimages%2F5%2F5b%2FYuri_death_scene_3.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20171112093758&h=ea96a625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5b2380050f3c6900a32b814dfda44af681b4d9a","tid":721057,"uid":163149,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"睇完幾想搵黎玩"},{"pid":"99bd50a3bb4297c68429fe8d71fa2b202c14788f","tid":721057,"uid":137556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a5b2380050f3c6900a32b814dfda44af681b4d9a","tid":721057,"uid":163149,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"睇完幾想搵黎玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"8638cf58febc1d733ba7502de3ee2981818afaba","tid":721057,"uid":43884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:26:14.000Z","msg":"有乜咁好玩"},{"pid":"806449afcb17506cd54742247bbeac42bac7e4fa","tid":721057,"uid":80463,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"99bd50a3bb4297c68429fe8d71fa2b202c14788f","tid":721057,"uid":137556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a5b2380050f3c6900a32b814dfda44af681b4d9a","tid":721057,"uid":163149,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"睇完幾想搵黎玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"+1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:27:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/698780/Doki_Doki_Literature_Club/?curator_clanid=31468181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F698780%2FDoki_Doki_Literature_Club%2F%3Fcurator_clanid%3D31468181&d=7euVI9lNcrrryKnQ5M9xm4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=53001a95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/698780/Doki_Doki_Literature_Club/?curator_clanid=31468181</a>"},{"pid":"c93b27d672900993098f2ec10b4d406715a231b8","tid":721057,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"